<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>API Boilerplate — Production-Ready REST + GraphQL + Realtime | ZOO</title>
<meta name="description" content="3 production API boilerplates: REST, GraphQL, Realtime. TypeScript, Node.js, Prisma, Redis, Docker. Auth, tests, CI/CD. $39.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0a0a0b; --surface: #12121a; --surface2: #1a1a26; --border: #2a2a3a;
  --border-hover: #3a3a4e; --text: #e8e8f0; --text2: #8888a0; --text3: #55556a;
  --accent: #06b6d4; --accent2: #22d3ee; --accent-glow: rgba(6,182,212,0.3);
  --warm: #f59e0b; --gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4, #6366f1);
  --font-body: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: var(--font-body); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

.nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(10,10,11,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
.nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.nav-logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; background: var(--gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; }
.nav-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 8px 20px; background: var(--accent); color: #000; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; transition: all 0.3s var(--ease); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--accent-glow); }
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent2); transform: translateY(-1px); }

.hero { padding: 140px 24px 80px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero-glow { position: absolute; top: -120px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 700px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(6,182,212,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
.hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
.hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; background: rgba(6,182,212,0.1); color: var(--accent2); border: 1px solid rgba(6,182,212,0.2); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 56px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.hero h1 .highlight { background: var(--gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
.hero p { color: var(--text2); font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.65; }
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s var(--ease); font-family: var(--font-body); }
.btn-primary { background: var(--gradient); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px var(--accent-glow); }
.btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 40px var(--accent-glow); }
.btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: var(--border-hover); }

.quickstart { max-width: 600px; margin: 48px auto 0; text-align: left; }
.quickstart pre { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-x: auto; color: var(--text2); }

.section { padding: 80px 24px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.section-header h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.section-header p { color: var(--text2); font-size: 17px; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }

.boilerplates-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
.bp-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; transition: all 0.3s; }
.bp-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(6,182,212,0.1); }
.bp-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.bp-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.bp-card p { color: var(--text2); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
.bp-features { list-style: none; margin-top: 14px; }
.bp-features li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text3); padding: 3px 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.bp-features li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--accent); font-size: 12px; }

.features-full { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
.feature-item { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 22px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.feature-item .check { color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.feature-item span { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text2); }

.deploy-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
.deploy-item { padding: 10px 20px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text2); }

.pricing-card { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--surface); border: 2px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 24px; padding: 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(6,182,212,0.12); }
.pricing-badge { position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--gradient); color: #fff; padding: 6px 24px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; white-space: nowrap; }
.pricing-card h3 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-top: 8px; }
.pricing-amount { margin: 20px 0; }
.pricing-amount .currency { font-size: 28px; vertical-align: super; }
.pricing-amount .value { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em; }
.pricing-amount .period { color: var(--text2); font-size: 14px; }
.pricing-features { list-style: none; margin: 24px 0; text-align: left; }
.pricing-features li { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text2); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
.pricing-features li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.pricing-card .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; padding: 18px; font-size: 17px; }
.pricing-guarantee { margin-top: 14px; color: var(--text3); font-size: 13px; }

.faq-grid { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; gap: 12px; }
.faq-item { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; }
.faq-item h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.faq-item p { color: var(--text2); font-index: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }

.cta-final { text-align: center; padding: 64px 32px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px; margin: 0 24px 80px; max-width: 1100px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.cta-final::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(6,182,212,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
.cta-final h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative; }
.cta-final p { color: var(--text2); font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; }
.cta-final .btn { position: relative; }

.footer { text-align: center; padding: 48px 24px; color: var(--text2); font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent); margin: 0 auto; max-width: 1100px; }

@media (max-width: 768px) { .hero { padding: 120px 20px 60px; } .section { padding: 60px 20px; } .pricing-card { padding: 32px 24px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="https://zootechnologies.com" class="nav-logo">ZOO</a>
    <a href="#pricing" class="nav-cta">Get All 3 APIs — $39 →</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">⚡ TypeScript · Node.js · Prisma · Docker</div>
    <h1>Your Next API.<br><span class="highlight">Already Built.</span></h1>
    <p>3 production-ready API boilerplates: REST, GraphQL, and Realtime. Auth, tests, CI/CD, Docker — everything you need to ship today. Stop reinventing the wheel.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-primary">Get All 3 — $39</a>
      <a href="#boilerplates" class="btn btn-ghost">See What's Inside ↓</a>
    </div>
    <div class="quickstart">
      <pre><span style="color:var(--text3);"># 15 minutes to production</span>
git clone https://github.com/zootechnologies/api-boilerplate
cd api-boilerplate/rest-api
cp .env.example .env
docker compose up -d
<span style="color:var(--text3);"># API running at localhost:3000</span>
<span style="color:var(--text3);"># Swagger docs at localhost:3000/docs</span></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section" id="boilerplates">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>3 Boilerplates, 0 Excuses</h2>
    <p>Pick the one that fits your stack — or use all three.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="boilerplates-grid">
    <div class="bp-card">
      <div class="bp-icon">🌐</div>
      <h3>REST API Boilerplate</h3>
      <p>Express.js / Fastify with everything you need. The foundation for any web service.</p>
      <ul class="bp-features">
        <li>JWT auth + OAuth2 (Google, GitHub)</li>
        <li>RBAC + request validation (Zod)</li>
        <li>Rate limiting + throttling</li>
        <li>Swagger/OpenAPI documentation</li>
        <li>Unit + integration tests (Vitest)</li>
        <li>Pluggable: Stripe, S3, BullMQ</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bp-card">
      <div class="bp-icon">🔷</div>
      <h3>GraphQL API Boilerplate</h3>
      <li>Apollo Server with schema-first design. Real-time subscriptions & federation ready.</p>
      <ul class="bp-features">
        <li>Schema-first with code generation</li>
        <li>WebSocket subscriptions</li>
        <li>Apollo Federation support</li>
        <li>Dataloader for N+1 prevention</li>
        <li>File uploads via GraphQL</li>
        <li>Auth directives + role guards</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bp-card">
      <div class="bp-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Realtime API Boilerplate</h3>
      <p>WebSocket-based with presence, rooms, and pub/sub. The backbone for live features.</p>
      <ul class="bp-features">
        <li>WebSocket + fallback to SSE</li>
        <li>Presence tracking (online/offline)</li>
        <li>Rooms + channel system</li>
        <li>Pub/Sub with Redis adapter</li>
        <li>Reconnection + heartbeat</li>
        <li>Horizontal scaling ready</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Everything Included</h2>
    <p>Not a skeleton. A complete, working API.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="features-full">
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>User registration / login / password reset</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Email verification</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>API key management</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Webhook system (outbound)</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Admin panel scaffolding</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Stripe integration (subscriptions)</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>File upload (S3 / Cloudflare R2)</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Queue system (BullMQ)</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Cron job scheduler</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Prometheus metrics endpoint</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Structured logging (Pino)</span></div>
    <div class="feature-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions)</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Deploy Anywhere</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="deploy-grid">
    <span class="deploy-item">▲ Vercel (serverless)</span>
    <span class="deploy-item">🚂 Railway</span>
    <span class="deploy-item">🎨 Render</span>
    <span class="deploy-item">☁️ AWS ECS/Fargate</span>
    <span class="deploy-item">🌊 DigitalOcean</span>
    <span class="deploy-item">🐳 Self-hosted Docker</span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section" id="pricing">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Ship Faster. Pay Once.</h2>
    <p>3 production APIs. One price. Lifetime updates.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pricing-card">
    <div class="pricing-badge">📦 All 3 Boilerplates</div>
    <h3>API Boilerplate Collection</h3>
    <div class="pricing-amount">
      <span class="currency">$</span><span class="value">39</span>
      <div class="period">one-time payment</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="pricing-features">
      <li>REST API boilerplate (Express/Fastify)</li>
      <li>GraphQL API boilerplate (Apollo Server)</li>
      <li>Realtime API boilerplate (WebSocket)</li>
      <li>JWT + OAuth2 authentication</li>
      <li>RBAC + request validation + rate limiting</li>
      <li>Stripe subscriptions + webhooks + file upload</li>
      <li>BullMQ queues + cron jobs + Prometheus metrics</li>
      <li>Unit + integration tests with Vitest</li>
      <li>Docker + Docker Compose + CI/CD</li>
      <li>API documentation (Swagger/OpenAPI)</li>
      <li>Deployment guides for 6 platforms</li>
      <li>Future updates included</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/checkout.html?product=api-boilerplate&price=39" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;padding:18px;font-size:17px;">
      Get Instant Access — $39
    </a>
    <div class="pricing-guarantee">🔒 Secure payment via Stripe · 30-day money-back guarantee</div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-header"><h2>FAQ</h2></div>
  <div class="faq-grid">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Do I need to know TypeScript?</h4>
      <p>Yes, basic TypeScript knowledge is required. The code is fully typed with detailed comments.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Can I use this commercially?</h4>
      <p>Absolutely. Full commercial license. Build your SaaS, ship it, monetize it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>How do I get updates?</h4>
      <p>All future updates are included free. Watch the GitHub repo and pull when new versions drop.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h4>Does it work with my frontend?</h4>
      <p>Yes — the REST and GraphQL APIs work with any frontend. React, Vue, Svelte, Next.js, whatever you use.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="cta-final">
  <h2>Stop Building Boilerplate.<br>Start Building Features.</h2>
  <p>3 production APIs. Auth, tests, CI/CD, Docker. Everything. $39 one-time.</p>
  <a href="/checkout.html?product=api-boilerplate&price=39" class="btn btn-primary">Get All 3 APIs — $39</a>
  <div style="margin-top:16px;color:var(--text3);font-size:13px;">🔒 Payment secured by Stripe · Instant access · 30-day guarantee</div>
